There's nothing we can do.

293
00:17:28,359 --> 00:17:29,490
How long has it been?

294
00:17:30,450 --> 00:17:31,130
What?

295
00:17:32,980 --> 00:17:34,580
Since I last met you, Taichi.

296
00:17:35,270 --> 00:17:36,150
Well.

