00:18:07,070 --> 00:18:08,800
I suddenly came to understand.

302
00:18:09,770 --> 00:18:10,430
About what?

303
00:18:13,520 --> 00:18:15,570
I really wanted to see you.

304
00:18:17,230 --> 00:18:17,990
What?

305
00:18:19,140 --> 00:18:20,070
What do you mean?

306
00:18:20,350 --> 00:18:22,080
