307
00:18:31,790 --> 00:18:32,550
Yes.

308
00:18:36,450 --> 00:18:36,960
Huh?

309
00:18:42,570 --> 00:18:46,850
When I saw you enjoy your meal, Taichi,

310
00:18:47,620 --> 00:18:48,930
I felt at ease.

311
00:18:54,620 --> 00:18:56,150
What are you talking about?

312
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:04,100
When I heard you say

