00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:06,800
it was delicious,

314
00:19:09,950 --> 00:19:11,830
I became happy too.

315
00:19:23,410 --> 00:19:24,250
I hate it.

316
00:19:27,570 --> 00:19:28,090
What?

317
00:19:32,020 --> 00:19:33,220
I won't be able to hear

318
00:19:35,730 --> 00:19:37,190
