319
00:19:42,460 --> 00:19:43,260
I hate it.

320
00:19:57,430 --> 00:19:58,930
Are you okay, Kouhei?

321
00:20:05,650 --> 00:20:06,190
Kouhei?

322
00:20:15,900 --> 00:20:18,030
Did you go to the restaurant you work at

323
00:20:19,550 --> 00:20:20,820
with Miho?

324
00:20:21,770 --> 00:20:22,890
What?

325
00:20:31,080 --> 00:20:31,920
I see.

326
00:20:37,380 --> 00:20:38,780
Why did you keep it from me

327
00:20:41,280 --> 00:20:42,810
when I asked you about this?

328
00:20:47,250 --> 00:20:48,950
I didn't mean to keep it from you.

329
00:20:48,950 --> 00:20:50,480
What did you two talk about?

330
00:20:51,800 --> 00:20:52,560
Tell me.

331
00:20:59,090 --> 00:20:59,970
Amazing.

332
00:20:59,990 --> 00:21:01,660
Just like in this novel.

