336
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:09,200
She did everything for her poor boyfriend. It's so touching.

337
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:11,890
I've always wanted to communicate with people with sign language,

338
00:21:11,890 --> 00:21:13,880
