339
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:16,080
He's like a character from that story.

340
00:21:18,380 --> 00:21:18,880
Hey.

341
00:21:24,430 --> 00:21:25,010
No.

342
00:21:32,230 --> 00:21:33,360
I'm not telling you.

343
00:21:42,950 --> 00:21:43,910
Sorry.

344
00:22:56,870 --> 00:22:57,730
I'll leave now.

345
00:22:57,760 --> 00:22:58,800
Oh.

346
00:22:58,820 --> 00:23:00,350
Are you going to work today?

347
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:01,660
It's the new semester.

348
00:23:07,280 --> 00:23:08,340
Is he okay?

349
00:23:18,820 --> 00:23:19,600
I'm sorry

350
00:23:20,750 --> 00:23:22,610
I never replied to your messages.

351
00:23:24,590 --> 00:23:27,560
Actually, I wasn't angry.

352
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:30,500
Yoko. Yasu.

353
00:23:31,030 --> 00:23:31,660
Oh.

354
00:23:31,680 --> 00:23:32,480
Good morning.

355
00:23:32,550 --> 00:23:33,820
Did you see Kouhei?

356
00:23:34,300 --> 00:23:35,070
Sugihara?

357
00:23:35,270 --> 00:23:36,320
No.

358
00:23:36,610 --> 00:23:38,010
Let me know if you see him.

359
00:23:38,840 --> 00:23:40,840
Okay. But don't ride your bike here.

360
00:23:41,740 --> 00:23:42,340
Actually,

361
00:23:43,690 --> 00:23:45,130
I should thank you.

362
00:23:47,780 --> 00:23:49,200
You really helped me a lot

363
00:23:50,490 --> 00:23:51,800
by staying by my side.

364
00:23:52,430 --> 00:23:53,160
Kouhei.

365
00:23:54,790 --> 00:23:55,700
Kouhei.

